mantralaya mahatme ( kannada : ಮಂತ ರಾಲಯ ಮಹಾತ ಮೆ ) is a 1966 indian kannada film directed by t. v. singh thakur , based on sri raghavendra vijaya written by rajaguru rajacharya , and stars rajkumar in the role of raghavendra swami , a hindu saint who lived in the 17th century india .   udaykumar , ramesh , jayanthi and kalpana appear in pivotal roles in the film .